review: I thought it was gonna be like yea, it's another one that's gonna be boring. The content is actually more eye-opening for me and I didn't expect myself to learn so much from this book. It talks about the different levels show how you view yourself currently.

title: The 10X Rule: The Only Difference Between Success and Failure
author: Grant Cardone
review: This book inspired me to "Level UP" myself. The book itself was valuable to me, but the author is not a great influencer in my opinion. He might be a great property saleman, but I don't agree with the way he took money from his followers. The book itself though, definitely brings value to me as a person.
